I love Ryan with all of my heart no doubt but we are always in a fight and I just dont know how to deal with this. Plus I do like josh and I want things to work out but I am not gonna have a boyfriend for a while until I know if I am gonna take Ryan back or not and then even longer after that because if I dont take him back then I have to give me and him both time to get over each other. Gosh I just dont know what to do I mean I love him I really do I just dont know if we need to be together. We still talk all of the time and we will still be friends but I dont know if I can handle to see him with someone else that is why I think that part of me still wants to be with him, the other part of me thinks that we argue so much that we make each other miserable. It is like we want this to work so much that we put so much effort into it and then it doesnt ever work! One of us is always unhappy! Well I am gonna go for now because all this talk of Ryan is making me want to cry!

Well I havent wrote in a while I have been grounded! I have been through so much in the last three weeks! Me and Ryan broke up and I am so upset I feel like all I was put on the earth to do is make mistakes the only thing I think I have ever done right is get Ryan to be a part of my life and have the friends that I have like Kara and Brittany. Ryan means so much to me and well I hate being me without him! It is really hard! Well, I went to his house today and we talked a little bit about some stuff and then I dont know why but I guess that he realized that I really love him and want him to be a part of my life and he reached out and started to run his fingers through my hair then he grabbed my hand and of course I couldnt hold back the tears. I havent really slept in like three weeks. I keep having this same dream over and over. Me and Ryan are sitting in his room and he is looking at me and he just grabbs my hand and then starts to hold me and then I usually wake up...but today he did this and I just kept wanting to pinch myself and make sure it wasnt another dream. I was the happiest person alive! I really hope that we work out I love him so much! He means the world to me! I would do anything for him! Well I am gonna go to bed I am tired and tonight I cant wait to get to sleep so I can see his face. Night!

<marquee/> True love does conquer all <marquee/>

I cant quit thinking about how bad I hurt Ryan and I cant quit thinking about all kinds of things! stupid shit I guess like when Ryan ask me why I did the things I did and I dont have an answer for him I know exactly how bad it hurts to not have an answer for the most important questions because...My dad...well He left home when I was like four ever since then he has never been there and has always promised me things and never given them to me and when I ask him why he left what the hell is going wrong the only answer that I get is I dont know and that makes me think its my faught because I am such a big Fuck-up...why not just fuck one more thing up? Then I wonder what I would have felt like if I got ridiculed and snareled at everytime I was seen walking with the person who cheated on me if I were in his shoes? 
What the fuck? How could I have been so fucking stupid? How could I do that to someone I love soooo much? HOW? These are the questions that Ryan wants answered and funny thing is I want them answered too because I dont have a fucking clue! I dont know what the Fuck was running through my head!
